## 1. Evaluation License

Permission is granted to download, inspect, compile, and test this software
for evaluation and security research purposes, free of charge.

Redistribution of the source code, in whole or in part, is permitted provided
that the above copyright notice and this license are included.

## 2. WLTIOS Integration License

Integration into the WLTIOS security OS, including compilation, bundling into
the WLTIOS initramfs, and execution on WLTIOS targets, is permitted.

## 3. Restrictions

- This software may NOT be sold or distributed as a standalone commercial product.
- Removal of tamper-evident logging, signature verification, or kill-switch
  mechanisms is prohibited in deployed configurations.
- The `update_signing.key` (private Ed25519 key) in this repository is for
  DEVELOPMENT ONLY. It MUST be replaced with a production key before deployment.

